56 Sanidassanattika, Atītattika
Sanidassanattika, Atītattika
65.
203Nasanidassanasappaṭigho napaccuppanno dhammo anidassanaappaṭighassa paccuppannassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
204Ārammaṇe cha, adhipatiyā cha, anantare samanantare tīṇi, upanissaye cha, natthiyā vigate tīṇi.
